snippet: Erin Mielzynski of Canada won a World Cup slalom in Ofterschwang, Germany, for the first World Cup victory of her career.
abstract: Canadian skier Erin Mielzynski wins World Cup slalom in Ofterschwang, Germany, for the first World Cup victory of her career; other winter sports noted.
lead_paragraph: Erin Mielzynski of Canada won a World Cup slalom in Ofterschwang, Germany, for the first World Cup victory of her career.

headline.seo: Canadian Wins First World Cup Skiing Race
